What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 111 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 111 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: A good, relatively small section that exposes you to a lot of resources for the arts at Yale.

This isn't a real art class. Take it credit/d if you want to take it at all, because it is a huge workload and may not be the gut you want it to be. If you want to visit all of Yale's cool paper places, then take it, but it is not in anyway preparation for the art or art history major.
